      <title>Ladbrokes 母公司 Entain 任命行业资深人士 Isaacs 为首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/ladbrokes-owner-entain-names-industry-veteran-isaacs-as-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国体育博彩公司 Entain Plc 已任命 Gavin Isaacs 为首席执行官，接替临时首席执行官 Stella David，后者在活动人士的压力下于 12 月上任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/ladbrokes-owner-entain-names-industry-veteran-isaacs-as-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 06:51:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
